title: NFL ATL: Are Manning and Brady's windows closing?
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Are Manning and Brady's windows closing?
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- breaks down what the future may hold for Tom Brady and Peyton Manning.  Are the two quarterbacks trending toward quiet twilight years or on the verge of late-career glory?
